In this statement, the President congratulates the Afghans on their participation in the historic elections, which promise to bring about the first democratic transfer of power in Afghanistan's history. He commends the Afghan people, security forces, and elections officials on the voter turnout and emphasizes the importance of these elections for securing Afghanistan's democratic future and continued international support. The President also pays tribute to the Americans who have sacrificed to support the Afghan people. The United States remains committed to supporting a sovereign, stable, unified, and democratic Afghanistan and looks forward to partnering with the new government chosen by the Afghan people.